system requirements:
===================
- multi core reasonably up to date Linux system (Met Norway: ubuntu ixenial, 40 cores, 128GB RAM)
- storage of ~1.7 TB per year
- bash 4
- nco installed >= version 4.7 (earlier versions need small adjustments in the code; --trd switch)
  recent versions can be installed from conda
- cdo installed >= version 1.9 (earlier versions might work as well)
  recent versions can be installed from conda

